text: Takayoshi Matsushita is a Japanese archer. He was born on 30 January 1953. Matsushita competed at the 1984, 1988, 1996, and the 2000 Summer Olympics.Takayoshi MatsushitaTakayoshi MATSUSHITA == References == Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese archers Category:Olympians for Japan
